Definition: the quality of needing attention and affection and reassurance to a marked degree
Example: he recognized her neediness but had no time to respond to it
Synonyms: adj, all, demanding, needy, quality, the, of, needing, attention, and, affection, reassurance, to, a, marked, degree, he, recognized, her, but, had, no, time, respond, it
Category: noun.attribute
